title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 135] Mod Revival, New Wave, Psychedelic
description:
What we have on part 135 are four obscure bands and four awesome records for those who are discovering the other side of the 80s and expanding their musical knowledge of this truly amazing decade. Enjoy and seed!


Darius And The Magnets - In The Valley Of Dreams [1982] 

Style: New Wave, Psychedelic Rock 


Industrials - Industrials [1980] 

Style: New Wave, Synthwave


LMNOP - Elemen Opee Elpee [1986]

Style:Mod Revival, Alternative Rock, Power Pop 


Necessaries - Event Horizon [1982]

Style: New Wave, Power Pop
